      "body": "<!--e57a25ab6845829454e8d69fc972939a-->\n\nThe following sections might be updated with supplementary metadata relevant to reviewers and maintainers.\n\n<!--021abf342d371248e50ceaed478a90ca-->\n### Reviews\nSee [the guideline](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#code-review) for information on the review process.\nA summary of reviews will appear here.\n<!--5faf32d7da4f0f540f40219e4f7537a3-->\n### LLM Linter (✨ experimental)\n\n\n\nPossible typos and grammar issues:\n\n- `CheckWitnessMalleation : invalid witness reserved value size` -> `CheckWitnessMalleability : invalid witness reserved value size` [“Malleation” is an unidiomatic/likely misspelling; “malleability” is the standard term and improves comprehension.]\n- `CheckWitnessMalleation : witness merkle commitment mismatch` -> `CheckWitnessMalleability : witness merkle commitment mismatch` [Same spelling issue as above.]\n- `CheckWitnessMalleation : unexpected witness data found` -> `CheckWitnessMalleability : unexpected witness data found` [Same spelling issue as above.]\n\n\n\n\nPossible places where named args for integral literals may be used (e.g. `func(x, /*named_arg=*/0)` in C++, and `func(x, named_arg=0)` in Python):\n\n- `CreateValidTransaction(/*input_transactions=*/{m_coinbase_txns[0]}, /*inputs=*/{COutPoint(m_coinbase_txns[0]->GetHash(), 0)}, /*input_height=*/1, /*input_signing_keys=*/{coinbaseKey}, /*outputs=*/{CTxOut(1, CScript() << OP_TRUE)}, /*feerate=*/std::nullopt, /*fee_output=*/std::nullopt)` in `src/test/validation_block_contextual_tests.cpp`\n- `CreateValidTransaction(/*input_transactions=*/{m_coinbase_txns[tx_idx]}, /*inputs=*/{COutPoint(m_coinbase_txns[tx_idx]->GetHash(), 0)}, /*input_height=*/1, /*input_signing_keys=*/{coinbaseKey}, /*outputs=*/{CTxOut(49 * COIN, CScript() << OP_TRUE)}, /*feerate=*/std::nullopt, /*fee_output=*/std::nullopt)` in `src/test/validation_block_contextual_tests.cpp`\n- `CreateValidTransaction(/*input_transactions=*/{m_coinbase_txns[0]}, /*inputs=*/{COutPoint(m_coinbase_txns[0]->GetHash(), 0)}, /*input_height=*/1, /*input_signing_keys=*/{coinbaseKey}, /*outputs=*/{CTxOut(1, CScript())}, /*feerate=*/std::nullopt, /*fee_output=*/std::nullopt)` in `src/test/validation_block_contextual_tests.cpp`\n- `SignatureHash(multisig, mtx, 0, SIGHASH_ALL, 1 * COIN, SigVersion::BASE)` in `src/test/validation_block_stateful_tests.cpp`\n- `SignatureHash(p2pkh, mtx, 0, SIGHASH_ALL, 1 * COIN, SigVersion::BASE)` in `src/test/validation_block_stateful_tests.cpp`\n- `SignatureHash(p2wpkh_script, mtx, 0, SIGHASH_ALL, wrong_value, SigVersion::WITNESS_V0)` in `src/test/validation_block_stateful_tests.cpp`\n\n\n\n<sup>2026-04-04 01:43:05</sup>\n",
